    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/03d5eba76c8caad6fd8cdfb2b3c1bf00.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=171 /></span><br>LONGTAIL!! is an action-adventure game inspired by PlayStation 2 and GameCube-era classics. It’s a celebration of the nostalgic titles from the 2000s that many of us grew up with.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as the lizard creature Longtail and embark on an adventure through a world filled with mysteries to solve, challenges to overcome, and new friends to meet.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/1752be7d7d12912c620a88b8fbdef69a.poster.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/1752be7d7d12912c620a88b8fbdef69a.webm?t=1750870351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/306b5f187b38b8cabd2e6f522b6d30a5.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You spend your days swimming, fishing, and sleeping in your hammock. With no care in the world, you feel content with the way things are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But one day, your peaceful life comes to a sudden end when your brother goes missing. Those around you begin to suspect that something terrible has happened to him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You leave your comfortable life behind to search for your brother, embarking on an adventure that will change everything you thought you knew about the world, and about yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/fbe4d63d49017738590011f8900311d5.poster.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/fbe4d63d49017738590011f8900311d5.webm?t=1750870351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/9b9b635ff4d848bd0afb455f9761858c.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover powerful abilities and use them to your advantage as you journey through the world. Learn new skills that give you the upper hand in combat, help you reach new areas, and uncover hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/d1ed48a74e18f03d564539dd31d89cb5.poster.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/d1ed48a74e18f03d564539dd31d89cb5.webm?t=1750870351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/2dff68a0d21a3392b52d4475b62c91b1.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is filled with ancient bastions for you to explore. Venture deeper into these mysterious structures left behind by your ancestors and uncover what's hidden deep within. Each bastion offers new challenges for you to overcome and brings you closer to the truth of your brother's whereabouts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/6ae3304e9103628394582d4c3e179826.poster.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/6ae3304e9103628394582d4c3e179826.webm?t=1750870351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1179640/extras/54b9e726e57064bca9abcfdf5d87a57b.avif?t=1750870351\" width=640 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will travel through many beautiful places on your journey. Every biome is unique, with different wildlife and various ways for you to explore. Surf the dunes with your sandboard, ride your llama mount through lush forests, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
